  - Target: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 780ff7812ed42474e9d4c2b4982cc385, type: 2}
    <Line>k__BackingField: <GiveItem(Bow)>
  - Target: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 780ff7812ed42474e9d4c2b4982cc385, type: 2}
    <Line>k__BackingField: "\uC790 \uC774\uAC70 \uBC1B\uACE0 \uB2E4\uC2DC \uC5F4\uC2EC\uD788
